--   Π X :[id] ★ → Π x :[id] X → Π x :[id.1] X → X
--   Π X :[] ★ → Π x :[X :[id] = X] X → Π x :[X :[id] = X] X → X
-- What's the difference?
--   Not the last. If something is intended to work in any context, all substs should start in id.
